Nick Talman s father is a dirty banker being hunted by the FBI. He gives Nick $2 million to move around so it can t be traced. Nick uses the money to invest in Izzy s revolutionary online foreign exchange idea. But when the people whose money was stolen start showing up, Izzy and Nick are forced to work together with criminals. Each one of them has a vision of accomplishing their own dreams. The premise of the show is promising; if you can get past the unwarranted sex scenes. The show also stars Kenyan-born actor Edi Gathegi. Star Rating: 3/5